text: Rodenas may refer to: * Ródenas, a municipality in Teruel, Spain * Rodenäs, a municipality in Schleswig-Holstein, Germany * Alejandra Rodenas (born 1963), Argentine lawyer, judge, professor, and politician * Clementina Ródenas (born 1949), Spanish politician ==See also== * Inés Rodena (1905–1985), Cuban writer
